{"tid":180590,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟應該嘈or忍?","createTime":"2017-03-31T04:25:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-31T06:18:22.000Z","uid":97887,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"23d478819f99e4cb7a7450310930a37d2021ffbd","tid":180590,"uid":97887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T04:25:28.000Z","msg":"無100%夾嘅人，一對情侶，點都有少少對對方嘅不滿<br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲會揀嘈?揀忍?<br />\n<br />\n聽過有情侶係從來無嘈過，但突然分左手，原來「冰封?尺，非一日之寒」<br />\n<br />\n又聽過有情侶嘈我5太多，最後頂唔順分手<br />\n<br />\n咁你地選擇係點?<br />\n<br />\n我自己揀左嘈，所以同佢一有不滿就嘈，唔忍<br />\n但嘈完會有共識，對大家瞭解多左<br />\n缺點係嘈太多，大家都好煩"},{"pid":"ee4d36fad6fbb430fe8035cbcf0cc7809cef55d6","tid":180590,"uid":36045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T04:27:39.000Z","msg":"平心靜氣講道理<br />\n但對手成日會發惡"},{"pid":"86d40a5d6ef08722779d28e1f4ee50d8fc1aadf5","tid":180590,"uid":97887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T04:28:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>平心靜氣講道理<br />\n但對手成日會發惡</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBtw,講道理睇時間<br />\n對方激動嘅就唔好講住<br />\n等冷靜先講"},{"pid":"0610550ddf931884dbc64631da71619b17866085","tid":180590,"uid":61543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T04:32:57.000Z","msg":"一不滿就要做愛<br />\n做完先講<br />\n樓主同我做愛ok?"},{"pid":"b4f4ee37eea6a3b1d4bc8106e8f3f41154025841","tid":180590,"uid":59795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T04:35:10.000Z","msg":"就係嘈太多所以分手，宜家我諗如果個陣我就佢多啲唔嘈交，結局會唔會改變呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c406cbfc2411ae7292d385d67bf7f2722e9de2aa","tid":180590,"uid":97887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T04:35:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一不滿就要做愛<br />\n做完先講<br />\n樓主同我做愛ok?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實你係咪覺得好好笑?"},{"pid":"c045bdff5170f1dc17d19f8b6cfaff9a70a08a3c","tid":180590,"uid":61543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T04:36:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一不滿就要做愛<br />\n做完先講<br />\n樓主同我做愛ok?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實你係咪覺得好好笑?</blockquote><br />\n其實都唔係講笑"},{"pid":"b7df1d6e8cc57a767055c544b333c68865e6f486","tid":180590,"uid":97887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T04:37:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就係嘈太多所以分手，宜家我諗如果個陣我就佢多啲唔嘈交，結局會唔會改變呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁如果一方面就，有日都係會爆<br />\n除非你肯定你就到一世，以後唔爆"},{"pid":"036c45600f557ee25157d94211b90b2399d8a605","tid":180590,"uid":97887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T04:37:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一不滿就要做愛<br />\n做完先講<br />\n樓主同我做愛ok?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實你係咪覺得好好笑?</blockquote><br />\n其實都唔係講笑</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你認就得<br />\n我報驚"},{"pid":"a741b454ba45cb4d8132489e08934f9a62cc4536","tid":180590,"uid":31442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T04:40:20.000Z","msg":"支持嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見過人地一直sweet到爆 但有日突然分左<br />\n因為有一方忍無可忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n被分個個又無奈又唔知點<br />\n見到佢都覺得慘"},{"pid":"c051faa29fc9c0b1d7f025d3caf73876a8f4376c","tid":180590,"uid":59795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T04:41:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>就係嘈太多所以分手，宜家我諗如果個陣我就佢多啲唔嘈交，結局會唔會改變呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁如果一方面就，有日都係會爆<br />\n除非你肯定你就到一世，以後唔爆</blockquote><br />\n咁的確係我發佢脾氣多啲既，我都覺係我問題，但宜家想改也太遲了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a77d0db1bd1440b0f8a1e4bdbaee82a55be9aba9","tid":180590,"uid":97887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T04:44:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支持嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見過人地一直sweet到爆 但有日突然分左<br />\n因為有一方忍無可忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n被分個個又無奈又唔知點<br />\n見到佢都覺得慘</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我就係嘈嘅<br />\n嘈得多又煩"},{"pid":"b4bd3b8fbb050a63056d90418e559416d4eff363","tid":180590,"uid":97887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T04:45:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>就係嘈太多所以分手，宜家我諗如果個陣我就佢多啲唔嘈交，結局會唔會改變呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁如果一方面就，有日都係會爆<br />\n除非你肯定你就到一世，以後唔爆</blockquote><br />\n咁的確係我發佢脾氣多啲既，我都覺係我問題，但宜家想改也太遲了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 咁如果比巴打搭時光機<br />\n你會寧願忍一世?"},{"pid":"0e6889fb9bd8e84356373fcadddc2dd7accf112b","tid":180590,"uid":59795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T04:47:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>就係嘈太多所以分手，宜家我諗如果個陣我就佢多啲唔嘈交，結局會唔會改變呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁如果一方面就，有日都係會爆<br />\n除非你肯定你就到一世，以後唔爆</blockquote><br />\n咁的確係我發佢脾氣多啲既，我都覺係我問題，但宜家想改也太遲了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 咁如果比巴打搭時光機<br />\n你會寧願忍一世?</blockquote><br />\n可能係分左手之後睇通左，諗返以前可能因為小事而嘈好無謂，唔係忍唔忍，係睇化了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"275752c9c17cd14679aba0d7fb2586c8a7df258b","tid":180590,"uid":97887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T04:49:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>就係嘈太多所以分手，宜家我諗如果個陣我就佢多啲唔嘈交，結局會唔會改變呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁如果一方面就，有日都係會爆<br />\n除非你肯定你就到一世，以後唔爆</blockquote><br />\n咁的確係我發佢脾氣多啲既，我都覺係我問題，但宜家想改也太遲了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 咁如果比巴打搭時光機<br />\n你會寧願忍一世?</blockquote><br />\n可能係分左手之後睇通左，諗返以前可能因為小事而嘈好無謂，唔係忍唔忍，係睇化了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點睇化....."},{"pid":"2a04d63a98775259f047ea0243c4a9c0431c9fa6","tid":180590,"uid":59795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T04:51:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>就係嘈太多所以分手，宜家我諗如果個陣我就佢多啲唔嘈交，結局會唔會改變呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁如果一方面就，有日都係會爆<br />\n除非你肯定你就到一世，以後唔爆</blockquote><br />\n咁的確係我發佢脾氣多啲既，我都覺係我問題，但宜家想改也太遲了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 咁如果比巴打搭時光機<br />\n你會寧願忍一世?</blockquote><br />\n可能係分左手之後睇通左，諗返以前可能因為小事而嘈好無謂，唔係忍唔忍，係睇化了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點睇化.....</blockquote><br />\n係自己問題唔怪得對方，所以佢離開都係我問題...<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">打打下都眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"b80d92a8b487f396456007695812e3c6345aba88","tid":180590,"uid":97887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T04:55:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>就係嘈太多所以分手，宜家我諗如果個陣我就佢多啲唔嘈交，結局會唔會改變呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁如果一方面就，有日都係會爆<br />\n除非你肯定你就到一世，以後唔爆</blockquote><br />\n咁的確係我發佢脾氣多啲既，我都覺係我問題，但宜家想改也太遲了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 咁如果比巴打搭時光機<br />\n你會寧願忍一世?</blockquote><br />\n可能係分左手之後睇通左，諗返以前可能因為小事而嘈好無謂，唔係忍唔忍，係睇化了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點睇化.....</blockquote><br />\n係自己問題唔怪得對方，所以佢離開都係我問題...<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">打打下都眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSorry,唔應該問<br />\n不過可能講出黎舒服d.....<br />\n唔好屈係心<br />\n搵d樹loan 傾下"},{"pid":"5e259280460b5f7365d39eb1579d6787a7d4a6b5","tid":180590,"uid":56636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T04:55:39.000Z","msg":"其實最重要既factor係：點嘈，同嘈完會做咩"},{"pid":"b38d2eac759755337c619f0d289b52c5b9f1efe6","tid":180590,"uid":83904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T04:56:38.000Z","msg":"一定係嘈<br />\n嘈完再夾個解決方法<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係儲下儲下就好易爆炸"},{"pid":"45fe37571d4ffcdf74348500c815813b65d40c86","tid":180590,"uid":43518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T05:00:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一定係嘈<br />\n嘈完再夾個解決方法<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係儲下儲下就好易爆炸</blockquote><br />\n嘈完唔改都係無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d94b60d33608e0946609f92c7db9c873987f9069","tid":180590,"uid":31442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T05:11:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>支持嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見過人地一直sweet到爆 但有日突然分左<br />\n因為有一方忍無可忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n被分個個又無奈又唔知點<br />\n見到佢都覺得慘</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我就係嘈嘅<br />\n嘈得多又煩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都見過嘈太多所以分<br />\n不過咁 我覺得係對方唔夠愛<br />\n愛自己多過對方<br />\n剩係為自己著想<br />\n一有唔滿意就嘈<br />\n一味屌鳩人而自己就毫無改善<br />\n嘈到心死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 分完個女都冇乜失戀feel<br />\n可能我睇唔出啦/佢冇表現出黎<br />\n覺得單身係正確嘅選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd483b3b0feb45183de8b797beb7e02550ab0b6a","tid":180590,"uid":83904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T05:12:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一定係嘈<br />\n嘈完再夾個解決方法<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係儲下儲下就好易爆炸</blockquote><br />\n嘈完唔改都係無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一步一步改囉<br />\n唔改始終有原因<br />\n學胡官講 咩都可以溝通 睇你肯唔肯姐"},{"pid":"3c163703753f506b92796e92e99ae8ea7303f5af","tid":180590,"uid":2111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T05:14:17.000Z","msg":"唔係嘈 而係溝通 <br />\n唔好到失去左你先識得復悔用錯方式"},{"pid":"c765370f521c4eb1cac1d26f5a5b4f8be2b375c4","tid":180590,"uid":43518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T05:14:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一定係嘈<br />\n嘈完再夾個解決方法<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係儲下儲下就好易爆炸</blockquote><br />\n嘈完唔改都係無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一步一步改囉<br />\n唔改始終有原因<br />\n學胡官講 咩都可以溝通 睇你肯唔肯姐</blockquote><br />\n嘈完對方唔出聲，唔認有錯<br />\n就算自己肯溝通，對方唔肯係無用<br />\n所以嘈過一次就算，唔好忍直接分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ac944bdf76b5dd47904b08f328d77ebc533fb23","tid":180590,"uid":90301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T05:19:28.000Z","msg":"我覺得系傾。<br />\n當下千其唔可以嘈，因為激動嘅時候容易講錯嘢。<br />\n一定要傾番，唔可以當件事冇咗"}]}